<SUBJECT>
<P>
<s docid="LA020289-0065" num="28" wdcount="19"> POLITICAL APPOINTMENTS; BUSH, GEORGE; UNITED STATES -- AMBASSADORS; UNITED STATES -- EMBASSIES -- CHINA; LILLEY, JAMES R; ARONSON, BERNARD</s>
